---
/**
 * Studio Manifesto — replaces generic “about”; 2-col + glass + GSAP (site.ts).
 */
---

<section
  data-studio-manifesto
  class="relative z-10 px-6 py-16 md:px-8 md:py-24"
  aria-labelledby="studio-manifesto-heading"
>
  <div
    class="studio-manifesto-glass mx-auto max-w-6xl rounded-2xl border border-zinc-900/10 bg-white/55 px-6 py-12 shadow-[0_24px_80px_-24px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] backdrop-blur-[10px] md:px-12 md:py-16 lg:px-14 lg:py-20"
  >
    <div
      class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-20 lg:items-start"
    >
      <!-- Headline -->
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <h2
          id="studio-manifesto-heading"
          data-manifesto-headline
          class="manifesto-headline max-w-[20ch] text-[clamp(2rem,5vw,4.75rem)] font-black uppercase leading-[0.9] tracking-[-0.03em] text-zinc-950"
        >
          We don&apos;t just build sites. We architect assets.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Signal blocks + CTA -->
      <div class="min-w-0 space-y-10 md:space-y-12">
        <article data-manifesto-signal class="border-b border-zinc-900/10 pb-10 md:pb-12">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.35em] text-zinc-500">Signal 01</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-950 md:text-xl">
            Reframe.
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 md:text-base">
            We strip the noise from legacy brands to reveal the authority underneath. Positioning is
            engineering.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article data-manifesto-signal class="border-b border-zinc-900/10 pb-10 md:pb-12">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.35em] text-zinc-500">Signal 02</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-950 md:text-xl">
            Deploy.
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 md:text-base">
            We turn raw concepts into mission-critical software. From City Pulse to your next SaaS, we
            ship at scale.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article data-manifesto-signal class="border-b border-zinc-900/10 pb-10 md:pb-12 last:border-0 last:pb-0">
          <p class="font-mono text-[10px] font-semibold tracking-[0.35em] text-zinc-500">Signal 03</p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-zinc-950 md:text-xl">
            Audit.
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-zinc-600 md:text-base">
            We identify the &apos;leakage&apos; in your digital presence. Data-driven strategy to ensure
            zero-friction growth.
          </p>
        </article>

        <div data-manifesto-cta class="pt-2">
          <a
            href="/consultation"
            class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-zinc-950 pb-0.5 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-zinc-950 transition-colors hover:border-zinc-500 hover:text-zinc-600"
          >
            START THE AUDIT
            <span
              class="inline-block transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5"
              aria-hidden="true"
            >
              →
            </span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto-headline {
    background-image: linear-gradient(
      105deg,
      #09090b 0%,
      #52525b 42%,
      #18181b 50%,
      #52525b 58%,
      #09090b 100%
    );
    background-size: 220% auto;
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    color: transparent;
    /* Fallback if clip unsupported */
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  @supports not (background-clip: text) {
    .manifesto-headline {
      color: #09090b;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: inherit;
      background: none;
    }
  }
</style>
